videos.description: John Wolford pass intercepted Sean Chandler return for no gain to the WFrst 47
videos.headline: Wake Forest throws an interception on opening drive

videos.description: On the ensuing play after intercepting Wake Forest, Temple QB Phillip Walker throws a 48-yard touchdown pass to Adonis Jennings to give the Owls the first lead of the game.
videos.headline: Temple converts off Wake Forest's TO with 48-yard TD

videos.description: Wake Forest QB John Wolford hits a wide-open Cam Serigne over the middle of the field for a 41-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Wake's Wolford finds wide-open receiver for 41-yard TD

videos.description: Wake Forest caps a quick drive with John Wolford throwing a short pass to Tabari Hines, who takes it 20 yards to the end zone for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Hines scores 20-yard TD

videos.description: Dom Maggio punt for 37 yds , Sean Chandler returns for no gain to the Temp 12
videos.headline: Wake Forest recovers muffed punt

videos.description: Wake Forest's Cade Carney takes the ball and bounces off a Temple defender at the goal line to score an 11-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Carney muscles into end zone for TD

videos.description: Future Temple head coach Geoff Collins discusses anticipation of being the head coach
videos.headline: Future Temple head coach Geoff Collins discusses anticipation of being the head coach

videos.description: Phillip Walker pass intercepted Duke Ejiofor return for 1 yd to the Temp 39
videos.headline: Wake Forest gets interception off tip drill

videos.description: Wake Forest's Matt Colburn pushes against the Temple defense and just gets the ball over the goal line to give the Demon Deacons a 31-7 lead.
videos.headline: Colburn powers in to extend Wake Forest lead

videos.description: Wake Forest head coach Dave Clawson discusses high powered offense in 1st half
videos.headline: Wake Forest head coach Dave Clawson discusses high powered offense in 1st half

videos.description: Temple head coach Ed Foley discusses QB's hand injury
videos.headline: Temple head coach Ed Foley discusses QB's hand injury

videos.description: Needing a spark in the second half, Temple gets one when Adonis Jennings makes the catch and then races through a pair of tackles to the house for a 58-yard touchdown for the Owls.
videos.headline: Temple starts second half quickly with 58-yard TD
